value.string: Welcome home to this beach front condominium located in the central area of Maui known as Maalaea. Just steps to the Pacific Ocean and the longest (4.5 miles) beach on Maui. This one bed one bath has carpet and tile flooring. Open floor plan makes it feel spacious. Ocean views from the lanai. Walking distance to Maui Ocean Center, Maui Sports and Water Park, restaurants, shopping, surfing, snorkeling, fishing, whale watching, and boat adventures from the Maalaea Harbor. Hono Kai is made up of 46 units on one tropically landscaped acre. The lovely pool and BBQ area are on the ocean. One 20-pound dog or cat is permitted. Buyer to do their own due diligence. This unit is in a long term rental and requires 48 hour notice to show. Fee Interest is available for purchase at $66,000 plus closing costs. List price does not include fee purchase.

Nice Oceanfront 2 bedroom, 2 bath Leasehold Condo with magnificent mountain & ocean views. Property is being sold via an online marketing event. Submit offers directly to Homesearch.com or Auction.com. Any financed offers require a pre-qualification from Greenlight Loans. 888-668-5832. Sold in AS IS" condition. Buyer to conduct their own Due Diligence. No Disclosure Statements will be provided.
